text.tspan: Home Time - Lights out at midnight
Bristol Register Office - We are getting
married in a small ceremony with our
families at 2pm. Meet us to celebrate as
Welsh Back - Party starts as we all
board the boat to Beeses. There
will be bubbles (and a bar on board)
Beeses Riverside Bar - Dinner will be
around 5pm followed by a band so
bring your dancing shoes and eat
